PYTHON +3.14

Install pip packages:

-m pip install numpy pandas yfinance pyyaml


Run the model: Select date-
\folder.venv\Scripts\python.exe SCurve\scurve\run.py --asof YYYY-MM-DD --config SCurve\config\scurve_config.yaml

In powershell:
Example:
--asof 2026-03-03 --config SCurve\config\scurve_config.yaml

Output csv files will appear in a run/YYYYMMDD folder outside of the scurve folder.

Example:

run/
  20260303/
    fit_diagnostics.csv
    portfolio_weights.csv
    scores.csv
